#: ../../user/hardware/certified-hardware/nitropc-pro.rst:45
#: c81dc8757e354ae7b1fa8145d31a1a29
msgid ""
"Of special note for Qubes users, the NitroPC Pro features a combined PS/2"
" port that supports both a PS/2 keyboard and a PS/2 mouse simultaneously "
"with a Y-cable (not included). This allows for full control of dom0 "
"without the need for USB keyboard or mouse passthrough. Nitrokey also "
"offers a special tamper-evident shipping method for an additional fee. "
"With this option, the case screws will be individually sealed and "
"photographed, and the NitroPC Pro will be packed inside a sealed bag. "
"Photographs of the seals will be sent to you by email, which you can use "
"to determine whether the case was opened during transit."
msgstr ""

